00:03:02.610 --> 00:03:02.850
I can't give up after coming so far...!

00:03:02.850 --> 00:03:06.860
Somehow or other, I have to get Saori to listen...

00:03:06.860 --> 00:03:11.860
If you say that what I've said is too heavy, then I'll share half of the burden with you.

00:03:11.860 --> 00:03:18.810
That's why... that's why, please... Can you listen to everything I have to say?

00:03:18.810 --> 00:03:21.010
...Kyousuke-shi...

00:03:21.010 --> 00:03:24.530
Why are you doing so much for my sake...

